parameters:
\bustMoveHome[2, 30]\nc<Senpai>Saki, you know today is evaluation day, right? Are you okay
with the quota?

\nc<Saki>It's a close call... but it's a bit difficult with just
promotional activities.

\nc<Senpai>I took the time to teach you, so I expect at least that much
from you.

\nc<Demon Tribe Employee>Has everyone gathered? You all know today is evaluation day,
right?
\nc<Demon Tribe Employee>This team... there are no gaps this time either.
\nc<Saki>(Senpai is smiling... but somehow her expression is scary)

\nc<Demon Tribe Employee>Meary of the internal strife... even as a team leader, is
this all you can do?

\bustMsgExp[1, 1]\nc<Demon Tribe Employee>I ordered at least a 10% surplus for this term. Are you
trying to make me laugh? How long do you think you can stay
as a team leader?

\bustMsgExp[2, 0]\nc<Senpai>My apologies. There has been some training for the
newcomers.

\nc<Demon Tribe Employee>Excuses again? Come to my place later. We need to have a
talk.
\nc<Demon Tribe Employee>Really... they never listen, what a pain.

\nc<Lewd Demon Employee>Good work, Senpai. That one always sucks up to the
executives...

\nc<Senpai>It's fine. You understand, don't you? Yes, good work to
everyone for this term.

\nc<Senpai>I'll inform you about the next term's quota later, so make
sure to plan meticulously. As I always say, if you're
dispatched, it's your own responsibility. Got it?
\nc<???>Please... forgive me! I'm just a little short!
\nc<Security Guard>Quiet. Just follow me without saying a word.

\nc<???>But, I have a favor owed to me! If only that could be
repaid...

\nc<Security Guard>Besides, even if there was a favor owed, do you think that
person would just quietly return it? You're finished here,
so just follow me quietly!
\nc<Lewd Demon Employee>Don't worry about it... it's business as usual.
\nc<Lewd Demon Employee>In fact, our team has a very high survival rate...

\nc<Saki>Then, the person who was taken away on my first day of work
was...?
\nc<Lewd Demon Employee>She wouldn't listen to the Senpai and was stubborn...

\nc<Lewd Demon Employee>In the end, she couldn't even achieve 50% of her quota,
right?

\nc<Lewd Demon Employee>She kept saying she'd report us and all that, but if reports
were an issue, this company wouldn't have lasted till now.
\nc<Lewd Demon Employee>Anyway, Saki, you be careful too.
\bustMsgExp[2, 0]\nc<Senpai>Enough chit-chat. Or what, do you have the luxury to chat?

\nc<Senpai>Oh, Saki has a business trip to a client starting this
Friday.
\nc<Saki>Eh?! A business trip? I'm not mentally prepared yet...

\nc<Senpai>After three months of work, you should be able to handle a
job on your own. How long do you plan to just distribute
flyers?

\nc<Senpai>From this term on, your quota will be the same as everyone
else's. Be prepared for that.

\nc<Saki>(A business trip to the client? What am I supposed to do
there?)

\TA[1]We have achieved this term's conditions. Magical power will
be collected.
\TA[1]The target for the next term is 40,000 magical power.
